item.title: Help Fast Please!
item.dc:creator: @z4mor4k_m1n1on z4mor4k m1n1on
item.description:
@z4mor4k_m1n1on wrote:

@echo off COLOR 08 title myscape compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_05\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_05\bin\java.exe" server pause

also go to my computer and on the left click system info and then click advanced then click enviroment variables and click new at teh top and for the top line put PATH and for the bottom line putC:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_05\bin ok click ok now click new and put in CLASSPATH and for bottom put CLASSPATH=C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_05\bin;%CLASSPATH%;.
